reviewText: I received this very quickly and I hope to do business in the future with this person.

This movie is great for children all ages! We have 5 girls and they LOVE the t.v. show. This is not the only Raven movie we have. It IS the first Raven movie we have bought from Amazon. I strongly recommend anyone with girls ages 5 up to teenagers to buy it. It is also a GREAT family movie!! Our whole family LOVES to watch Raven movies!!!

This DVD is the fourth That's So Raven DVD, which means the characters in the show has matured quite a bit. As we all know T'Keyah Keym?h is no longer on the show for some apparent  reason concerning that she felt her character wasn't making a big impact. But the show must go on! Raven-Symon? is now one of the new producers on the show, which I absolutely love. So let's support the That's So Raven crew and go purchase this DVD.

Me and my boyfriend were both BIG fans of the show That's So Raven. (He was a BIGGER fan than myself.) So, I decided to buy this DVD and all the other ones too. They're all a great buy. Especially when this show doesn't come on tv all that much anymore. :\ It's nice to have a collection of That's So Raven episodes that we can watch anytime we want. I ordered this and it came in on time. I had no issues with this product at all. I highly suggest buying this item. (:

I bought this set for my daughter as a birthday gift. She loves it! She grew up watching this show as a teen when it aired on the Disney channel and had been looking for it on DVD. It was really hard to find in stores and unfortunately it hasn't aired on any channels that we have access to including Netflix. So she was so surprised when she received this from me. I'm happy Amazon had this available and that it wasn't priced ridiculously like most sets are.
I'd recommend this as a gift to any body that grewup with this show and to Raven Symone fans. It has quirky innocent humor for all ages

This series is a very light hearted, funny one that's highly enjoyable.  ***Sadly, they did Not release the entire series.***  Only 4 or 5 episodes were put on 4 DVD releases.  But, for what it is, this is a very good DVD, ... just don't expect it to be the full Season.

i also bought this dvd of this show and i enjoyed it also. i liked this dvd of this show because of the sense of humor and all the disguises that raven ever wore on this show a lot of the costumes she ever wore on the show were funny.so like i just said in my last review i would recommend anyone who used to watched this show and enjoyed it to buy it. it is worth the wait. sincerly chrisfan.
